## ğŸ¯ Enforcement

**This rule is MANDATORY.**

Every AI assistant working on SPOTS must:
- âœ… Know this rule exists
- âœ… Follow it every time
- âœ… Update tracker when creating plans
- âœ… Verify entry was added correctly

**No exceptions.**

---

## ğŸ“ Checklist for New Plan Creation

**BEFORE creating plan:**

- [ ] Checked Feature Cross-Reference Matrix
- [ ] Used Decision Tree to determine placement
- [ ] Verified idea doesn't belong in existing plan
- [ ] Confirmed idea is substantial enough (3+ days)

**IF creating new plan:**

- [ ] Plan document created in `docs/` directory
- [ ] Plan document is complete and comprehensive
- [ ] Includes cross-references to related plans
- [ ] `MASTER_PLAN_TRACKER.md` updated with new entry
- [ ] Feature Cross-Reference Matrix updated
- [ ] All required fields included
- [ ] Entry in correct section
- [ ] Statistics updated
- [ ] "Last Updated" timestamp current
- [ ] Both files committed together

---

**Remember: The tracker is the single source of truth. Keep it current. Reference it always.**

